am\"}, {\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8965243798236152, \"rank\": 0.11311137481882236, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final leg\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 576}, {\"ngram\": \"a sprint finish\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as the Kiwis were creeping up, the States found another gear to claim gold for the first time in the men's fours since 1960, while the Kiwis crossed in second for silver and Great Britain bagged the bronze.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.102567279899714e-21, \"text\": \"Kiwis\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.102567279899714e-21, \"text\": \"Kiwis\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9966050881209174, \"rank\": 0.0032551552890277614, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the States\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"another gear\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's fours\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"second\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macdonald said the race was \\\"pretty intense\\\".\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Macdonald\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We knew it was going to be all guns blazing from the start, and we had to trust our best race and hope we would be satisfied crossing the line, and I think we did a really close job to that.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all guns\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"our best race\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"a really close job\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We feel like the Americans got a little bit of a lead at the start and then extended that through the middle and then in the last 500m we drew up to them and it was all go the last 500.\\\"\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Americans\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"a lead\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macdonald said the team \\\"gave it everything\\\" at the finish and were pleased with their efforts.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Macdonald\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"their efforts\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Americans have been a top crew all season and I think we can hold our heads high and be really proud of that.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.450261331484367e-14, \"text\": \"The Americans\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Americans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a top crew\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"our heads\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could see out of the corner of my eye we were drawing level with [the US crew] coming into that last bit and it was sort of all on again and we knew it was going to be a sprint, so we had been practising that and we had our minds on it.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9979985042994922, \"rank\": 0.0019802515879560494, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the corner\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"my eye\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"level\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1542}, {\"ngram\": \"that last bit\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"a sprint\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\"